{"id": "150114", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=150114", "title": "Frayed Blade", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Boss%20Soul%20Items%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;soul-transposed&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Katanas%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;katana&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=\"The%20Ringed%20City\"&gt;The Ringed City&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nObtained by transposing the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Darkeater%20Midir\"&gt;Soul of Darkeater Midir&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Ludleth%20of%20Courland\"&gt;Ludleth of Courland&lt;/a&gt; for 5,000 &lt;a href=\"Soul%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nWith a staggering requirement of 40 &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;, the Frayed Blade is one of the most difficult weapons to wield in the entire game. However, it has many characteristics that solidify its position as one of the best in its class.\nWith its innate &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage, the Frayed Blade is capable of chipping down opponents through shields, something that most katanas have trouble with. Furthermore, its &lt;a href=\"skill\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; provides it with unique offensive potential, as the shockwave can be used to hit opponents at range or catch them as they try to roll away, while the slash combo can inflict tremendous amounts of &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; build-up on an unprotected target or powerful stamina damage if blocked. In the hands of an aggressive player, the Frayed Blade is truly a force to be reckoned with.\nHowever, it is also one of the heaviest katanas in the game, and has very low durability much like the &lt;a href=\"Washing%20Pole%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Washing Pole&lt;/a&gt;. Care should be taken when using this weapon, and carrying &lt;a href=\"Repair%20Powder%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Repair Powder&lt;/a&gt; may be useful on extended forays.\nMoveset.\nMoveset is identical to that of the &lt;a href=\"Uchigatana%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Uchigatana&lt;/a&gt;, however its weapon arts are unique."}
