{"id": "7911", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=7911", "title": "Gauntlets of Thorns", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Gauntlets of Thorns are a &lt;a href=\"hands%20armor\"&gt;hands armor&lt;/a&gt; piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". They are part of the &lt;a href=\"Set%20of%20Thorns\"&gt;Set of Thorns&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nFound after defeating &lt;a href=\"Kirk%2C%20Knight%20of%20Thorns\"&gt;Kirk, Knight of Thorns&lt;/a&gt; for the third and final time, on a corpse near &lt;a href=\"Quelaag%27s%20Sister\"&gt;Quelaag's Sister&lt;/a&gt; in the dead end area.\nCharacteristics.\nThe\u00a0Gauntlets of Thorns\u00a0are resistant to\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and boast average defense for their &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt; when unupgraded, but have the potential of having good defenses when fully upgraded, being slightly stronger against\u00a0&lt;a href=\"slash\"&gt;slash&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0type attacks.\nDeals 20 physical damage when rolling into nearby enemies. The damage dealt is added together with any of the other pieces of armor from the set.\nAlso boosts damage dealt with gauntlets by 20%.\nUpgrades.\nRequires 200 &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
