{"id": "11193", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11193", "title": "Giant Leech", "text": "Giant Leeches are in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLocation.\nThey are found along the corners of\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Blighttown\"&gt;Blighttown&lt;/a&gt;'s Poison Swamp, opposite of &lt;a href=\"Quelaag%27s%20Domain\"&gt;Quelaag's Domain&lt;/a&gt;.\nDescription.\nGiant Leeches are able to lunge at their opponent from a distance. They can also spray a short ranged projectile that causes &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects\"&gt;poison&lt;/a&gt; buildup."}
