{"id": "112668", "revid": "33084951", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=112668", "title": "Gilleah the Hexer", "text": "Gilleah the Hexer is a in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLore.\nGilleah the Hexer was responsible for the creation of multiple &lt;a href=\"Hexes\"&gt;Hexes&lt;/a&gt; found in &lt;a href=\"Drangleic\"&gt;Drangleic&lt;/a&gt;. It is unclear where he originated from or when he was born, but he can possibly be attributed to the creation of &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Orb%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Dark Orb&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dark%20Hail\"&gt;Dark Hail&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Twisted%20Barricade\"&gt;Twisted Barricade&lt;/a&gt;, and &lt;a href=\"Repel\"&gt;Repel&lt;/a&gt;. He never took an apprentice, meaning that it's possible the Hexes he's attributed to creating may not have been created by him after all.\nHe may be the \"sorcerer at the brink of madness\" from &lt;a href=\"Oolacile\"&gt;Oolacile&lt;/a&gt;, the ancient ruined city where Hexes (or \"Abyss Sorceries\", as they were known in that time) were discovered."}
