{"id": "8090", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8090", "title": "Gold-Hemmed Black Hood", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Gold-Hemmed Black Hood is a piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Gold-Hemmed%20Black%20Set\"&gt;Gold-Hemmed Black Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nFound with the rest of the &lt;a href=\"Gold-Hemmed%20Black%20Set\"&gt;Gold-Hemmed Black Set&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Ceaseless%20Discharge\"&gt;Ceaseless Discharge&lt;/a&gt;'s room. Picking up this set will turn him hostile and trigger the &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; fight.\nCharacteristics.\nThis hood offers the second highest &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; Resist out of any non-upgraded headpiece in the game. Its Poison resistance is surpassed by the &lt;a href=\"Bloated%20Sorcerer%20Head\"&gt;Bloated Sorcerer Head&lt;/a&gt; and the fully upgraded &lt;a href=\"Painting%20Guardian%20Hood\"&gt;Painting Guardian Hood&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpgrades.\nCannot be reinforced.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
{"id": "8091", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8091", "title": "Gold-Hemmed Black Set", "text": "The Gold-Hemmed Black Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound on the corpse on the pedestal &lt;a href=\"Ceaseless%20Discharge\"&gt;Ceaseless Discharge&lt;/a&gt; is guarding, early in the &lt;a href=\"Demon%20Ruins\"&gt;Demon Ruins&lt;/a&gt;. Picking up the set will cause Ceaseless Discharge to become hostile.\nPlot.\nThe Gold-Hemmed Black Set is the uniform of the Daughters of Chaos. &lt;a href=\"Quelana%20of%20Izalith\"&gt;Quelana of Izalith&lt;/a&gt; wears it, and it is also worn by the hostile &lt;a href=\"Daughter%20of%20Chaos\"&gt;Daughter of Chaos&lt;/a&gt; found near the end of &lt;a href=\"Lost%20Izalith\"&gt;Lost Izalith&lt;/a&gt;. The set the player can obtain also belonged to one of the Daughters of Chaos, whose corpse is guarded by Ceaseless Discharge.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Gold-Hemmed Black Set offers some of the highest &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt; resistance in the game, as well as decent &lt;a href=\"Physical%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; defenses for light armor. However, it cannot be upgraded, and its Poison Resist is outclassed by the fully upgraded &lt;a href=\"Painting%20Guardian%20Set\"&gt;Painting Guardian Set&lt;/a&gt;."}
