le the weight. If the hit connects, the stumble animation does not come into play and the user moves as normal. This makes this weapon capable of gaining &lt;a href=\"Damage%20%28Dark%20Souls%29%23Sweet%2520Spot%2520Damage%2520Bonus\"&gt;Sweet Spot Damage&lt;/a&gt; bonus. "}
