{"id": "130970", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130970", "title": "Gotthard Twinswords", "text": "The Gotthard Twinswords are paired &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;straight swords&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in &lt;a href=\"Lothric%20Castle\"&gt;Lothric Castle&lt;/a&gt;, on the lifeless body of &lt;a href=\"Black%20Hand%20Gotthard\"&gt;Black Hand Gotthard&lt;/a&gt;, just before the entrance to the &lt;a href=\"Grand%20Archives\"&gt;Grand Archives&lt;/a&gt;. The body will only appear once the player has defeated the first three &lt;a href=\"Lords%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Lords of Cinder&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=\"Abyss%20Watchers\"&gt;Abyss Watchers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Aldrich%2C%20Devourer%20of%20Gods\"&gt;Aldrich&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Yhorm%20the%20Giant\"&gt;Yhorm&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Gotthard Twinswords are dual-wielded blades that offer a devastating &lt;a href=\"Skill\"&gt;weapon skill&lt;/a&gt;, very fast moveset, and an attack time that is ideal for combo attacks. One of its more noticeable characteristics is that it starts with D &lt;a href=\"Parameter%20Bonus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Strength%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dexterity%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt; respectively. Its scaling is equal throughout its reinforcement and tops out at C, making it an ideal candidate for quality builds.\nMoveset.\nDual Wield attack: Uses both blades in a unique moveset that is made up of broad slashes and thrusts.\nWeapon Art: Strong slash with both blades, if chained with a strong attack immediately after, will perform a combo.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with ."}
