{"id": "135193", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135193", "title": "Grave Warden Set (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Grave Warden Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Grave%20Warden%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Grave Wardens&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Cathedral%20of%20the%20Deep\"&gt;Cathedral of the Deep&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Untended%20Graves\"&gt;Untended Graves&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Grave Warden Set is specialized against &lt;a href=\"Slash\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; damage as well as &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; effects. It is very light and possesses generally poor physical defenses, particularly against &lt;a href=\"Strike\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; damage, though as mentioned above it is quite resistant to &lt;a href=\"Slash\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; damage. Its elemental defenses are impressive, particularly against &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; damage, however it has a severe vulnerability to &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt;.\nIt also possesses strong all-round &lt;a href=\"Negative%20Status%20Effects%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;status effect&lt;/a&gt; resistance, with the exception of &lt;a href=\"Frost\"&gt;Frost&lt;/a&gt; buildup, which it is extremely weak to."}
