{"id": "134922", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=134922", "title": "Great Heavy Soul Arrow (Dark Souls III)", "text": "Great Heavy Soul Arrow is a &lt;a href=\"Sorcery%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;sorcery&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nEffect.\nThe most powerful version of the basic &lt;a href=\"Soul%20Arrow%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Soul Arrow&lt;/a&gt;, and an enhanced version of &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Soul%20Arrow%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Heavy Soul Arrow&lt;/a&gt;. Fires a heavy soul arrow, dealing 2.42 times the &lt;a href=\"Catalysts%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;catalyst's&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Spell%20Buff\"&gt;Spell Buff&lt;/a&gt; as &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; damage. Has the same &lt;a href=\"casting%20time\"&gt;casting time&lt;/a&gt; as Heavy Soul Arrow, while dealing more damage.\nAs the large multiplier on a single damage instance allows it to easily break through low to moderate values of Magic defense on the target, reducing its effectiveness, Great Heavy Soul Arrow is the most efficient Sorcery in the game, in terms of damage-to-&lt;a href=\"Focus%20Points\"&gt;FP&lt;/a&gt; ratio, once reductions from defense and absorption are factored in.\n&lt;br&gt;"}
