{"id": "5110", "revid": "56333033", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5110", "title": "Great Lord Greatsword", "text": "The Great Lord Greatsword is a &lt;a href=\"Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;greatsword&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nThe Great Lord Greatsword is created by &lt;a href=\"Weapon%20Modification\"&gt;ascending&lt;/a&gt; any &lt;a href=\"Standard%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;Standard&lt;/a&gt; +10 &lt;a href=\"Greatswords%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;greatsword&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Ultra%20Greatswords\"&gt;ultra greatsword&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Straight%20Swords%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;straight sword&lt;/a&gt;, or &lt;a href=\"Daggers\"&gt;dagger&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Giant%20Blacksmith\"&gt;Giant Blacksmith&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Anor%20Londo\"&gt;Anor Londo&lt;/a&gt; with the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Gwyn%2C%20Lord%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Soul of Gwyn, Lord of Cinder&lt;/a&gt; and 5,000 &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Great Lord Greatsword has a fairly quick swing speed compared to other Greatswords and has good base damage. However, its stat &lt;a href=\"scaling\"&gt;scaling&lt;/a&gt; is quite poor. Additionally, its strong attacks, while particularly powerful, have very long windups during which the wielder is defenseless. Great Lord Greatsword does not deal &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;Fire Damage&lt;/a&gt; even though &lt;a href=\"Gwyn%2C%20Lord%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Gwyn&lt;/a&gt; deals Fire Damage with this sword. "}
{"id": "5061", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=5061", "title": "Great Lord Set", "text": "The Great Lord Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nPurchased from &lt;a href=\"Domhnall%20of%20Zena\"&gt;Domhnall of Zena&lt;/a&gt; after the player has defeated &lt;a href=\"Gwyn%2C%20Lord%20of%20Cinder\"&gt;Gwyn, Lord of Cinder&lt;/a&gt;, and started a &lt;a href=\"New%20Game%20Plus\"&gt;new game&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nThe set is worn by Gwyn, Lord of Cinder.\nCharacteristics.\nHas above average &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt; for a light set, also having remarkable &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28damage%20type%29\"&gt;lightning&lt;/a&gt; resistance. It is more resistant to &lt;a href=\"Strike\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Slash\"&gt;Slash&lt;/a&gt; attacks. Its flaw, however, is that it can't be &lt;a href=\"Armor%20Modification\"&gt;upgraded&lt;/a&gt;, being easily surpassed by other light armor sets."}
