{"id": "99956", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=99956", "title": "Charred Loyce Set", "text": "The Charred Loyce Set is a &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;heavy armor set&lt;/a&gt; in .\nAvailability.\nDropped by &lt;a href=\"Charred%20Loyce%20Knight\"&gt;Charred Loyce Knight&lt;/a&gt;s in &lt;a href=\"The%20Old%20Chaos\"&gt;The Old Chaos&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThis armor set is stat-wise nearly identical to its cleaner version, the &lt;a href=\"Loyce%20Set\"&gt;Loyce Set&lt;/a&gt;. However, it is slight &lt;a href=\"Weight\"&gt;heavier&lt;/a&gt;, provides very minute increases in certain &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;s, has nearly half its &lt;a href=\"durability\"&gt;durability&lt;/a&gt;, and possesses a better &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;fire&lt;/a&gt; resistance, yet lower &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;magic&lt;/a&gt; resistance.\nThis armor set also draws a comparison with the &lt;a href=\"Ivory%20King%20Set\"&gt;Ivory King Set&lt;/a&gt;, as it is essentially an overall upgrade to the Charred Loyce Set, albeit somewhat heavier."}
