{"id": "90602", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=90602", "title": "Chime of Screams", "text": "The Chime of Screams is a &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;sacred chime&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Crown%20of%20the%20Old%20Iron%20King\"&gt;Dark Souls II: Crown of the Old Iron King&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nTrade the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Nadalia%2C%20Bride%20of%20Ash\"&gt;Soul of Nadalia, Bride of Ash&lt;/a&gt; along with 20,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; to &lt;a href=\"Weaponsmith%20Ornifex\"&gt;Weaponsmith Ornifex&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Chime of Screams is the slowest casting tool in the game, with a speed of 25. Combined with the low cast speed is lackluster damage in both Dark and Lightning, resulting in average damage in both Hexes and Miracles. However, what makes the Chime of Screams a valuable chime is its ability to raise faith, inverse to the amount of faith the player has; Meaning players with more faith will receive less faith than someone with lower faith, at a maximum increase of +6. The best practical use is for players with low FTH to keep this in the hand opposite of their main casting tool, to raise their FTH to use spells with higher requirements, ignoring its casting abilities."}
{"id": "48146", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=48146", "title": "Chime of Want", "text": "The Chime of Want is a &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;sacred chime&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nReceived by trading &lt;a href=\"Weaponsmith%20Ornifex\"&gt;Weaponsmith Ornifex&lt;/a&gt; the &lt;a href=\"Soul%20of%20Nashandra\"&gt;Soul of Nashandra&lt;/a&gt; and 10,000 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nThe Chime of Want provides good scaling for both Lightning and Dark damage, making it an excellent &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;chime&lt;/a&gt; for players that meet its stat requirements.\nThe Chime of Want is the strongest &lt;a href=\"Sacred%20Chimes\"&gt;chime&lt;/a&gt; available for &lt;a href=\"Hexes\"&gt;Hexers&lt;/a&gt;, although &lt;a href=\"Caitha%27s%20Chime\"&gt;Caitha's Chime&lt;/a&gt; can be considered a side-grade to it due to its higher &lt;a href=\"Casting%20Speed\"&gt;Casting Speed&lt;/a&gt; and lower &lt;a href=\"Faith%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Faith&lt;/a&gt; requirement.\u00a0The Chime of Want loses to the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Chime\"&gt;Dragon Chime&lt;/a&gt; when it comes to &lt;a href=\"Miracle%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Miracles&lt;/a&gt;."}
