{"id": "135178", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135178", "title": "Conjurator Set", "text": "The Conjurator Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound on a corpse near the &lt;a href=\"Great%20Swamp%20Pyromancy%20Tome\"&gt;Great Swamp Pyromancy Tome&lt;/a&gt; on the &lt;a href=\"Road%20of%20Sacrifices\"&gt;Road of Sacrifices&lt;/a&gt;, between a large tree and a wall near the &lt;a href=\"Crucifixion%20Woods\"&gt;Crucifixion Woods&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nReturning from the previous two games, the Conjurator Set offers extremely high &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;poison&lt;/a&gt; resistance, making it a great choice to using during the swamp section of &lt;a href=\"Farron%20Keep\"&gt;Farron Keep&lt;/a&gt;. It also provides strong &lt;a href=\"elemental%20defense\"&gt;elemental defense&lt;/a&gt;, particularly against &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;. The set does not offer great protection against &lt;a href=\"physical\"&gt;physical&lt;/a&gt; attacks, however.\nTrivia.\nSimilar to its previous incarnations, this set's appearance differs greatly depending on the wearer's gender. If the wearer is male, it will appear coarse and have a yellowish color, with black pants. If the wearer is female, it will be grey with a cloth worn over the shoulders, reminiscent of a shawl, as well as a long, grey skirt."}
