{"id": "4915", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4915", "title": "Core of an Iron Golem", "text": " \nThe Core of an Iron Golem is a consumable item in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nAvailability.\nThe Core of an Iron Golem is dropped upon defeating the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Golem\"&gt;Iron Golem&lt;/a&gt;.\nGeneral information.\nThe Core of an Iron Golem can be used to ascend a &lt;a href=\"Gauntlets\"&gt;gauntlet type weapon&lt;/a&gt; +10 into the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Bone%20Fist\"&gt;Dragon Bone Fist&lt;/a&gt;, or an &lt;a href=\"Axes\"&gt;axe&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Greataxes\"&gt;greataxe&lt;/a&gt; +10 into the &lt;a href=\"Golem%20Axe\"&gt;Golem Axe&lt;/a&gt;.\nThe Core of an Iron Golem can also be consumed for 12,000 &lt;a href=\"souls\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt;, or fed to &lt;a href=\"Kingseeker%20Frampt\"&gt;Kingseeker Frampt&lt;/a&gt; for 8,000 souls."}
