{"id": "135179", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135179", "title": "Cornyx's Set", "text": "Cornyx's Set is an &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nLike most other cloth sets, Cornyx's Set has mediocre resistance against &lt;a href=\"physical%20damage\"&gt;physical damage&lt;/a&gt;, but high &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; resistance, particularly against &lt;a href=\"Fire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Fire&lt;/a&gt;. Its strongest attribute, however, is its extremely strong &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance, though conversely it is also quite weak to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frost\"&gt;Frost&lt;/a&gt;."}
