{"id": "135180", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=135180", "title": "Court Sorcerer Set", "text": "The Court Sorcerer Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nFound in the &lt;a href=\"Profaned%20Capital\"&gt;Profaned Capital&lt;/a&gt;.\nIn the toxic swamp area, climb up the ladder and into the building. The set is located on a corpse next to the central pillar, guarded by a &lt;a href=\"Monstrosity%20of%20Sin\"&gt;Monstrosity of Sin&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Mimic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Mimic&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nOffers poor &lt;a href=\"physical%20defense\"&gt;physical defense&lt;/a&gt;s, but strong &lt;a href=\"elemental\"&gt;elemental&lt;/a&gt; absorption. It can greatly mitigate &lt;a href=\"Lightning%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Lightning&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dark%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Dark&lt;/a&gt; damage, and has very high &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance. However, it is very weak to &lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Frost\"&gt;Frost&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"buildup\"&gt;buildup&lt;/a&gt;."}
