{"id": "134506", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=134506", "title": "Crimson Parma (Dark Souls III)", "text": "The Crimson Parma is a &lt;a href=\"Small%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Small Shield&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nAn early-game Small Shield that is available to the player upon stepping foot in &lt;a href=\"Firelink%20Shrine%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Firelink Shrine&lt;/a&gt; for the first time, the Crimson Parma has no major defining characteristics, save for its low attribute requirements. Like other Small Shields, it is at its weakest when used to block attacks, but makes up for this by having more and faster &lt;a href=\"Parry%20and%20Riposte%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;parrying&lt;/a&gt; frames than a &lt;a href=\"Medium%20Shields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Medium Shield&lt;/a&gt;. It has moderately respectable elemental defenses for its weight, and is most resilient against &lt;a href=\"Magic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;Magic&lt;/a&gt; attacks.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with ."}
