{"id": "8074", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=8074", "title": "Crimson Set", "text": "The Crimson Set is a &lt;a href=\"Light%20Armor%20Sets%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;light armor set&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;.\"\nAvailability.\nThis set is found in &lt;a href=\"Blighttown\"&gt;Blighttown&lt;/a&gt; near the wooden elevator and the exit to the &lt;a href=\"Valley%20of%20Drakes\"&gt;Valley of Drakes&lt;/a&gt;. It is located across a branch/bridge on a corpse with a chest containing the &lt;a href=\"Remedy\"&gt;Remedy&lt;/a&gt; spell next to it.\nPlot.\nThe set is worn by\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Ingward\"&gt;Ingward&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0and the other two sealers of New Londo, &lt;a href=\"Yulva\"&gt;Yulva&lt;/a&gt; and one of &lt;a href=\"Lautrec%20the%20Embraced\"&gt;Lautrec of Carim's&lt;/a&gt; unnamed companions, although said companion does not wear the head piece. The Mask of the Sealer symbolizes the resolve of the sealers to keep the seal shut and to demonstrate their atonement for those sacrificed in the process of sealing what is now the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"New%20Londo%20Ruins\"&gt;New Londo Ruins&lt;/a&gt;. The set that the player finds likely once belonged to Yulva, as her sorcery, &lt;a href=\"Remedy\"&gt;Remedy&lt;/a&gt;, is found with it.\nCharacteristics.\nThis armor set offers no &lt;a href=\"Poise%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poise&lt;/a&gt;. However, it gives good &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; resistance and good &lt;a href=\"Physical%20defense\"&gt;Physical defense&lt;/a&gt; for its &lt;a href=\"weight\"&gt;weight&lt;/a&gt;, as well as average &lt;a href=\"Poison%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Poison&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=\"Bleed%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;Bleed&lt;/a&gt; resistances. It also provides high\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Magic%C2%A0defense\"&gt;Magic\u00a0defense&lt;/a&gt; and average\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Lightning%C2%A0defense\"&gt;Lightning\u00a0defense&lt;/a&gt;, with the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Fire%C2%A0defense\"&gt;Fire\u00a0defense&lt;/a&gt; being slightly weaker. The\u00a0Crimson Set is slightly stronger against\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Strike\"&gt;Strike&lt;/a&gt;-type attacks."}
