{"id": "87995", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=87995", "title": "Crown of the Old Iron King", "text": "The Crown of the Old Iron King is the second episode of \"&lt;a href=\"The%20Lost%20Crowns\"&gt;The Lost Crowns&lt;/a&gt;\" downloadable content pack for \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\". It was released on August 26th, 2014.\nAccess.\nTo access the content, defeat the &lt;a href=\"Old%20Iron%20King\"&gt;Old Iron King&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Keep\"&gt;Iron Keep&lt;/a&gt; and proceed to the &lt;a href=\"Primal%20Bonfire\"&gt;Primal Bonfire&lt;/a&gt;. Use the altar behind the bonfire to travel to the starting area. Upon loading, the &lt;a href=\"Heavy%20Iron%20Key\"&gt;Heavy Iron Key&lt;/a&gt; will be added to the player's inventory, which grants access to Brume Tower.\nThis changes in the \"\" edition of the game; the Heavy Iron Key can be found inside of the door opened by the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Key\"&gt;Iron Key&lt;/a&gt;, near &lt;a href=\"The%20Last%20Giant\"&gt;The Last Giant&lt;/a&gt;'s boss room in the &lt;a href=\"Forest%20of%20Fallen%20Giants\"&gt;Forest of Fallen Giants&lt;/a&gt;."}
