{"id": "90949", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=90949", "title": "Crown of the Sunken King", "text": "The Crown of the Sunken King is the first episode of the \"&lt;a href=\"The%20Lost%20Crowns\"&gt;The Lost Crowns&lt;/a&gt;\" downloadable content pack for \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\". It was released on July 22nd, 2014.\nAccess.\nTo access the content, defeat &lt;a href=\"The%20Rotten\"&gt;The Rotten&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Black%20Gulch\"&gt;Black Gulch&lt;/a&gt; and proceed to the &lt;a href=\"Primal%20Bonfire\"&gt;Primal Bonfire&lt;/a&gt;. Use the altar behind the bonfire to travel to the starting area. Upon loading, the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Talon\"&gt;Dragon Talon&lt;/a&gt; will be added to the player's inventory.\nThis changes in the \"\" edition of the game; the Dragon Talon can be found on a body behind the 'Forgotten Door' unlocked with the &lt;a href=\"Forgotten%20Key\"&gt;Forgotten Key&lt;/a&gt;, at the bottom of the well in Majula. This door grants access to &lt;a href=\"Shulva%2C%20Sanctum%20City\"&gt;Shulva, Sanctum City&lt;/a&gt;."}
