{"id": "94221", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=94221", "title": "Dog Rat", "text": "Dog Rats are &lt;a href=\"Enemies%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;enemies&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nDog Rats, also called Mongrel Rats in some supplemental material, are ratlike beasts that are strangely canine in appearance. They are encountered only in &lt;a href=\"Doors%20of%20Pharros\"&gt;Doors of Pharros&lt;/a&gt;, one of the two domains ruled by the &lt;a href=\"Rat%20King%20%28character%29\"&gt;Rat King&lt;/a&gt;. They are often fought alongside other enemies and cause strong &lt;a href=\"Toxic%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Toxic&lt;/a&gt;, and minor &lt;a href=\"Petrification\"&gt;Petrification&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0&lt;a href=\"build-up\"&gt;build-up&lt;/a&gt; with their attacks."}
{"id": "129358", "revid": "5064773", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=129358", "title": "Domhnall", "text": ""}
{"id": "2304", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2304", "title": "Domhnall of Zena", "text": "Domhnall of Zena (\u30bc\u30ca\u306e\u30c9\u30fc\u30ca\u30eb) is a &lt;a href=\"merchant\"&gt;merchant&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\". He is voiced by , who also voiced the &lt;a href=\"Crestfallen%20Warrior\"&gt;Crestfallen Warrior&lt;/a&gt;.\nPlot.\nDomhnall is an eccentric peddler who sells rare crystallized &lt;a href=\"equipment\"&gt;equipment&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"boss\"&gt;boss&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Armor%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;armor&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0but only after the player defeats the corresponding boss.\nLore.\nDomhnall was born in &lt;a href=\"Zena\"&gt;Zena&lt;/a&gt;. but very little else is known about him aside from his fascination with trinkets and oddities. His wares include the &lt;a href=\"Weapons%20%28Dark%20Souls%29\"&gt;weapons&lt;/a&gt; wielded by the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Undead%20Crystal%20Soldier\"&gt;crystal hollows&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in &lt;a href=\"The%20Duke%27s%20Archives\"&gt;The Duke's Archives&lt;/a&gt;, suggesting that he may have previously visited or fled from there, or that he is capable of\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Crystal%20%28upgrade%20path%29\"&gt;crystallization&lt;/a&gt;. He also sells a copy of his &lt;a href=\"Adventurer%27s%20Set\"&gt;Armor Set&lt;/a&gt;, hinting that he may have robbed it, and that the set he wears may be stolen as well.\nStrategy.\nDomhnall attacks much like any other &lt;a href=\"NPC\"&gt;NPC&lt;/a&gt;. Fighting him at the Firelink Shrine can be dangerous with the cliffs on either side. However, the terrain can be exploited by kicking or forcing him off a ledge."}
