{"id": "70957", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=70957", "title": "Dragon Memories", "text": "The\u00a0Dragon Memories is a &lt;a href=\"Locations%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;location&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nLocation.\nAfter obtaining the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Ashen%20Mist%20Heart\"&gt;Ashen Mist Heart&lt;/a&gt; from the &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Dragon\"&gt;Ancient Dragon&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in the\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Shrine\"&gt;Dragon Shrine&lt;/a&gt;, go back to the &lt;a href=\"Duke%27s%20Dear%20Freja\"&gt;Duke's Dear Freja&lt;/a&gt; boss room and you will find a crystal lying right below the &lt;a href=\"dragon\"&gt;dragon&lt;/a&gt; hanging from the roof. Interacting with it will cause you to access a dragon memory.\nThe player will find themselves in a grey, foggy place. Explore a bit and you will find the corpse of what seems to be an &lt;a href=\"Everlasting%20Dragons\"&gt;Everlasting Dragon&lt;/a&gt;,\u00a0get close to it and you will obtain the &lt;a href=\"Ancient%20Dragon%20Soul\"&gt;Ancient Dragon Soul&lt;/a&gt;."}
