{"id": "47673", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=47673", "title": "Dragonrider Greatshield", "text": "The Dragonrider Greatshield is a &lt;a href=\"Greatshields%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;greatshield&lt;/a&gt;\u00a0in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nAfter defeating &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider\"&gt;Dragonrider&lt;/a&gt; you'll obtain a &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider%20Soul\"&gt;Dragonrider Soul&lt;/a&gt;. Take this soul to &lt;a href=\"Straid%20of%20Olaphis\"&gt;Straid of Olaphis&lt;/a&gt; and trade it along with 1,500 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; for one of four weapons: the Dragonrider Greatshield, &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider%20Twinblade\"&gt;Dragonrider Twinblade&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider%27s%20Halberd\"&gt;Dragonrider's Halberd&lt;/a&gt; or\u00a0&lt;a href=\"Dragonrider%20Bow\"&gt;Dragonrider Bow&lt;/a&gt;.\nCharacteristics.\nWith average &lt;a href=\"elemental%20defense\"&gt;elemental defense&lt;/a&gt;s and &lt;a href=\"stability\"&gt;stability&lt;/a&gt;, the Dragonrider Greatshield draws a comparison to the &lt;a href=\"Giant%20Shield\"&gt;Giant Shield&lt;/a&gt; from \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls\"&gt;Dark Souls&lt;/a&gt;\", in that both of them are roughly a \"jack-of-all-trades\" greatshield; it will work in all situations (save for &lt;a href=\"Petrification%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;petrification&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Curse%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Curse&lt;/a&gt; protection), but there will always be another shield or greatshield that gets the job done better."}
{"id": "59805", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=59805", "title": "Dragonrider Helm", "text": "&lt;onlyinclude&gt;\n&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;\nThe Dragonrider Helm\u00a0is a piece in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20II\"&gt;Dark Souls II&lt;/a&gt;\". It is part of the &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider%20Set\"&gt;Dragonrider Set&lt;/a&gt;.\nAvailability.\nSold by &lt;a href=\"Magerold%20of%20Lanafir\"&gt;Magerold of Lanafir&lt;/a&gt; for 7,200 &lt;a href=\"Souls%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;souls&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"New%20Game%20Plus%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;NG+&lt;/a&gt; after defeating the two &lt;a href=\"Dragonrider\"&gt;Dragonrider&lt;/a&gt;s in &lt;a href=\"Drangleic%20Castle\"&gt;Drangleic Castle&lt;/a&gt;.\nAlternatively, burning a &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20Ascetic\"&gt;Bonfire Ascetic&lt;/a&gt; on the &lt;a href=\"Threshold%20Bridge\"&gt;Threshold Bridge&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;bonfire&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Iron%20Keep\"&gt;Iron Keep&lt;/a&gt; and increasing its &lt;a href=\"Bonfire%20Intensity\"&gt;intensity&lt;/a&gt; to 2, will also cause him to sell it.\nUpgrades.\nRequires &lt;a href=\"Twinkling%20Titanite%20%28Dark%20Souls%20II%29\"&gt;Twinkling Titanite&lt;/a&gt; per upgrade.\n&lt;onlyinclude&gt;\n&lt;/onlyinclude&gt;"}
