{"id": "130273", "revid": "49243392", "url": "https://darksouls.fandom.com/wiki?curid=130273", "title": "Drang Twinspears", "text": "The Drang Twinspears are &lt;a href=\"Paired%20Weapons\"&gt;paired&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Spears%20%28Dark%20Souls%20III%29\"&gt;spears&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Dark%20Souls%20III\"&gt;Dark Souls III&lt;/a&gt;\".\nAvailability.\nDropped by the &lt;a href=\"Drang%20Knight\"&gt;Drang Knight&lt;/a&gt; who wields them in &lt;a href=\"Irithyll%20of%20the%20Boreal%20Valley\"&gt;Irithyll of the Boreal Valley&lt;/a&gt;, in the courtyard after &lt;a href=\"Pontiff%20Sulyvahn\"&gt;Pontiff Sulyvahn&lt;/a&gt;.\nUpgrades.\nReinforced with .\n&lt;br&gt;"}
